WEBVTT

01:44.250 --> 01:48.720
[A LOVER IN THE MORTAL WORLD]

01:49.680 --> 01:51.840
[Episode 2]

01:56.320 --> 01:57.200
Miss Ling?

02:03.350 --> 02:04.610
How did you get in here?

02:04.870 --> 02:05.790
And who

02:06.060 --> 02:07.090
let you in?

02:11.480 --> 02:13.550
I snuck in by myself.

02:13.680 --> 02:14.710
So now, just anyone can walk

02:14.710 --> 02:16.370
into my Tianlang Pass prison?

02:16.650 --> 02:17.740
It seems Huang Jian

02:17.770 --> 02:19.430
doesn't want his job anymore.

02:20.000 --> 02:20.790
No, no, no.

02:24.840 --> 02:26.700
I'm actually here to see Zhao Gao.

02:26.800 --> 02:28.120
This prison is heavily guarded.

02:28.120 --> 02:29.150
I couldn't have gotten in at all.

02:29.150 --> 02:31.050
But I saved Huang Jian's son before.

02:31.050 --> 02:32.450
And I begged him so hard.

02:32.870 --> 02:34.120
He softened up...

02:35.560 --> 02:36.680
and let me in.

02:36.950 --> 02:39.010
Then why are you looking for Zhao Gao?

02:39.400 --> 02:40.030
I...

02:40.630 --> 02:41.990
Do you still want to marry him?

02:41.990 --> 02:43.110
How could I?

02:43.140 --> 02:44.940
Then why are you looking for him?

02:47.790 --> 02:49.190
Not going to tell me, huh?

02:50.310 --> 02:51.430
I'll go ask Zhao Gao.

02:51.430 --> 02:52.890
He'll definitely tell me.

02:53.840 --> 02:54.280
You—

02:59.150 --> 03:00.000
General Xiao.

03:00.320 --> 03:00.960
Zhao Gao.

03:07.870 --> 03:09.680
You two...

03:11.610 --> 03:12.450
Xiao Chi,

03:12.550 --> 03:14.440
when are you going to let me out?

03:14.560 --> 03:15.240
I came here

03:15.480 --> 03:16.870
just to tell you about this.

03:16.870 --> 03:17.870
In half a month,

03:18.030 --> 03:19.579
you will be taken back to the capital.

03:19.579 --> 03:21.150
Then I will report to His Majesty

03:21.150 --> 03:22.190
about how you

03:22.190 --> 03:23.360
withheld military pay

03:23.360 --> 03:25.150
and forced Changmo women to marry you.

03:25.150 --> 03:25.680
Right.

03:25.860 --> 03:26.400
Also,

03:26.930 --> 03:29.110
your status as a special envoy
has been revoked.

03:29.110 --> 03:30.110
This token...

03:30.600 --> 03:31.600
I brought it over.

03:31.840 --> 03:32.970
Keep it as a memento.

03:36.590 --> 03:37.960
Xiao Chi!

03:40.680 --> 03:41.630
General Xiao.

03:41.910 --> 03:43.470
Lord Xiao!

03:43.630 --> 03:45.120
For the sake of the Grand Consort,

03:45.120 --> 03:46.650
please let me off this time.

03:46.690 --> 03:47.210
Well,

03:47.840 --> 03:49.120
I'll give you a way out.

03:49.590 --> 03:50.720
As long as you tell me

03:51.020 --> 03:53.180
why this girl beside me

03:53.800 --> 03:54.800
came to find you,

03:55.150 --> 03:57.210
I will plead with His Majesty for you.

03:57.230 --> 03:59.430
Perhaps you can get a lighter sentence.

04:00.900 --> 04:02.040
She said she was going to the capital

04:02.040 --> 04:03.960
and wanted to use my special envoy token
to pass the checkpoint.

04:03.960 --> 04:05.280
I said I would give it to her

04:05.280 --> 04:06.480
as long as she could rescue me.

04:06.480 --> 04:07.760
That's... that's all.

04:08.120 --> 04:08.800
Zhao Gao,

04:09.560 --> 04:10.310
do you know

04:10.590 --> 04:12.050
if she is a spy from Changmo

04:12.400 --> 04:13.750
and reaches the capital,

04:13.750 --> 04:16.680
both the city and His Majesty
will be in grave danger.

04:17.070 --> 04:18.390
I didn't collude with the enemy.

04:18.390 --> 04:20.220
I... I didn't know she was a spy.

04:20.240 --> 04:21.300
That's hard to say.

04:21.750 --> 04:22.610
How about this?

04:22.680 --> 04:23.720
I'll interrogate her myself

04:23.720 --> 04:25.010
for Lord Zhao.

04:30.270 --> 04:30.800
My Lord,

04:31.600 --> 04:32.570
it's getting late.

04:32.570 --> 04:33.690
We can only rest at this inn

04:33.690 --> 04:34.640
for the night

04:34.710 --> 04:37.070
and head to Tianlang Pass
early tomorrow morning.

04:37.070 --> 04:37.800
That works.

04:37.820 --> 04:40.360
You've all worked hard traveling
these past few days.

04:40.360 --> 04:42.620
Let's get a good rest at this inn tonight.

04:42.810 --> 04:43.420
Yes.

04:52.960 --> 04:54.290
Where is the innkeeper?

04:56.890 --> 04:57.350
Huo Ran.

04:57.900 --> 04:58.430
My Lord.

04:58.540 --> 04:59.340
Go take a look.

04:59.720 --> 05:00.270
Yes.

05:04.040 --> 05:07.640
Drunkenly holding the golden goblet
to invite the moon to drink.

05:08.310 --> 05:12.310
Half-parted lips asking
if my lover has arrived.

05:14.830 --> 05:16.910
Where are you from?

05:17.150 --> 05:19.040
The most prosperous place of Jinglan—

05:19.040 --> 05:19.770
the capital.

05:19.770 --> 05:21.060
The capital?

05:22.080 --> 05:23.210
That's a nice place—

05:24.600 --> 05:26.330
Moonlight flowing like water.

05:26.680 --> 05:28.270
Lanterns bright as day.

05:29.830 --> 05:31.390
Pity that I

05:31.630 --> 05:34.120
have never been to such
a prosperous place.

05:35.830 --> 05:37.230
May I ask

05:39.310 --> 05:40.710
how should I address you?

05:41.950 --> 05:44.360
You may call me

05:45.100 --> 05:45.740
Fei Zheng.

05:45.900 --> 05:47.700
A meeting is a matter of destiny.

05:47.750 --> 05:48.870
Guest,

05:49.140 --> 05:50.670
why don't you join me

05:50.970 --> 05:51.820
for a drink?

05:52.630 --> 05:53.310
Alright.

05:53.480 --> 05:54.740
I happen to be thirsty.

05:59.390 --> 06:00.240
Please.

06:05.720 --> 06:07.520
You can really hold your liquor.

06:07.920 --> 06:09.040
What's

06:09.190 --> 06:10.310
your name?

06:10.430 --> 06:11.490
My surname is Tang.

06:12.430 --> 06:13.680
You can call me

06:15.000 --> 06:16.000
Tang Zhaoxue.

06:16.360 --> 06:17.800
Tang Zhaoxue.

06:19.120 --> 06:21.380
To be an innkeeper here in Tianlang Pass,

06:21.720 --> 06:24.070
you must know this place very well.

06:24.240 --> 06:25.040
Of course.

06:25.430 --> 06:26.190
I wonder

06:26.430 --> 06:28.230
if I could ask you about someone.

06:28.430 --> 06:29.120
Go ahead.

06:30.510 --> 06:31.310
General Xiao,

06:31.940 --> 06:32.770
Xiao Chi.

06:33.510 --> 06:34.510
I wonder if you

06:35.030 --> 06:36.290
have ever heard of him?

06:37.280 --> 06:38.250
Him?

06:44.070 --> 06:46.070
He's the man all the women in the city

06:46.270 --> 06:47.920
dream of marrying.

06:51.940 --> 06:53.620
General Xiao, is this okay?

06:54.070 --> 06:55.130
Why wouldn't it be?

06:55.480 --> 06:56.720
With your skills, General,

06:56.720 --> 06:57.720
there's no need to lock the door

06:57.720 --> 06:59.070
to interrogate a woman.

06:59.170 --> 07:00.570
Just lock it when I tell you to.

07:00.570 --> 07:02.500
If she is really a spy from Changmo,

07:03.390 --> 07:05.120
we can't let her escape easily.

07:05.290 --> 07:05.940
By the way,

07:06.180 --> 07:07.190
without my orders,

07:07.190 --> 07:08.240
no one is allowed to come in.

07:08.240 --> 07:09.000
Yes, sir.

07:11.430 --> 07:12.560
This cell

07:12.750 --> 07:15.150
used to be a place
for interrogating spies.

07:15.870 --> 07:18.360
Though I've never used
these torture devices,

07:18.360 --> 07:19.390
Miss Ling,

07:19.640 --> 07:20.990
if you want to...

07:23.870 --> 07:25.600
I wouldn't mind giving it a try.

07:26.430 --> 07:28.430
I have been treating you.

07:28.840 --> 07:30.260
So I guess I've done you a favor.

07:30.260 --> 07:31.430
And I believe

07:31.720 --> 07:33.390
you are an honorable man

07:33.680 --> 07:36.010
and wouldn't torture me for a confession.

07:36.500 --> 07:37.650
That's not it.

07:38.190 --> 07:40.430
If you really are a spy from Changmo,

07:41.110 --> 07:42.350
then don't blame me

07:42.680 --> 07:44.800
for repaying kindness with hostility.

07:44.800 --> 07:46.600
It seems I can't hide it anymore.

07:47.680 --> 07:48.480
Alright.

07:48.640 --> 07:50.500
I will answer 3 of your questions.

07:50.630 --> 07:51.700
I will answer truthfully

07:51.700 --> 07:52.940
as long as you ask.

07:52.970 --> 07:54.240
Why are you going to the capital?

07:54.240 --> 07:55.000
To save someone.

07:55.000 --> 07:55.510
Save who?

07:55.510 --> 07:56.190
My brother.

07:57.159 --> 07:58.620
Only one question is left.

07:59.420 --> 08:01.350
Is she really the girl who saved me?

08:02.210 --> 08:03.240
Why can't I see a trace of the past

08:03.240 --> 08:05.070
in her eyes?

08:07.040 --> 08:08.070
Could she really be

08:08.070 --> 08:10.130
the one I've missed for over 10 years?

08:11.120 --> 08:13.180
But does she really not recognize me?

08:13.920 --> 08:15.000
What is

08:15.180 --> 08:16.350
your real name?

08:20.830 --> 08:21.720
Han Yunling.

08:22.240 --> 08:23.700
Thank you, Physician Han.

08:23.950 --> 08:25.750
I'm Physician Han Yunling.

08:27.800 --> 08:29.720
I've answered 3 of your questions.

08:29.720 --> 08:31.660
Could you answer 3 of mine?

08:33.000 --> 08:34.260
What do you want to ask?

08:34.270 --> 08:35.630
How can I leave the pass?

08:35.770 --> 08:37.289
It requires a border pass

08:37.530 --> 08:38.510
written by me personally.

08:38.510 --> 08:40.630
Then could you write a pass

08:40.669 --> 08:41.600
so I can leave?

08:41.720 --> 08:42.510
No.

08:42.840 --> 08:43.750
Why?

08:43.909 --> 08:45.390
Our countries have been at war for years.

08:45.390 --> 08:46.270
Changmo

08:46.520 --> 08:48.650
constantly sends spies into Jinglan.

08:48.960 --> 08:51.200
As the general guarding Tianlang Pass,

08:51.360 --> 08:52.150
how could I possibly give

08:52.150 --> 08:53.840
the written pass to a Changmo person

08:53.840 --> 08:55.170
of unknown background?

08:55.560 --> 08:58.220
If I were a bad person,
why would I save your life?

08:58.270 --> 08:59.810
You stayed at Tianlang Pass

08:59.840 --> 09:02.170
just to figure out
how to go to the capital.

09:02.390 --> 09:03.390
Am I right,

09:03.790 --> 09:05.270
Miss Han Yunling?

09:09.790 --> 09:10.750
If

09:11.270 --> 09:12.510
you can tell me

09:13.030 --> 09:14.200
your true identity

09:14.440 --> 09:15.390
and purpose,

09:15.680 --> 09:17.370
I might consider it.

09:18.960 --> 09:20.270
I am just

09:20.480 --> 09:21.460
an ordinary Changmo woman

09:21.460 --> 09:23.210
who knows a little medicine.

09:23.390 --> 09:24.630
I'm not a spy.

09:24.650 --> 09:26.550
And I don't know any spies, either.

09:26.550 --> 09:27.270
Okay.

09:28.370 --> 09:29.440
Then tomorrow,

09:29.810 --> 09:31.270
I will arrange for someone

09:31.740 --> 09:33.470
to send you out of Tianlang Pass

09:33.670 --> 09:34.870
and back to Changmo.

09:35.510 --> 09:37.040
What about your illness then?

09:37.040 --> 09:39.150
I'm the general of the border defense,

09:39.150 --> 09:41.320
and you being from Changmo
with an unknown background—

09:41.320 --> 09:42.510
to appease the troops,

09:42.510 --> 09:45.370
I cannot accept
your long-term medical treatment.

09:49.690 --> 09:51.410
Since you have made up your mind,

09:51.410 --> 09:52.600
there's nothing I can do.

09:52.600 --> 09:54.270
You're don't want to live.

09:54.570 --> 09:56.490
Don't blame my lack of medical skills.

09:56.490 --> 09:57.610
Of course not.

09:58.100 --> 09:59.390
I've been frail since childhood.

09:59.390 --> 10:00.630
Guarding Sirius Pass for years

10:00.630 --> 10:02.200
has already taken a toll on my body.

10:02.200 --> 10:03.440
Life and death—

10:03.870 --> 10:05.730
I've long since made peace with it.

10:05.730 --> 10:06.760
But I...

10:12.080 --> 10:12.960
All right.

10:13.550 --> 10:15.200
I will leave Tianlang Pass tomorrow.

10:15.200 --> 10:18.200
Let me treat you
one last time today.

10:19.150 --> 10:20.030
Now?

10:20.150 --> 10:21.030
Of course.

10:22.030 --> 10:23.360
Right here?

10:23.630 --> 10:25.270
This is the perfect place.

10:25.440 --> 10:26.970
Please give me your hand.

10:43.030 --> 10:44.090
What are you doing?

10:45.900 --> 10:47.430
What on earth are you doing?

10:48.120 --> 10:49.150
Please look.

10:49.580 --> 10:53.310
The cold poison in your body
has built up in your spleen and kidneys.

10:53.360 --> 10:54.480
Cold poison in the spleen

10:54.480 --> 10:55.880
causes loss of appetite.

10:56.270 --> 10:57.910
The kidneys are the foundation
of your constitution.

10:57.910 --> 11:00.030
When affected by cold poison,
it causes a pale face

11:00.030 --> 11:01.150
and cold limbs.

11:01.600 --> 11:03.080
After years of spreading,

11:03.360 --> 11:05.030
it has accumulated from your arms

11:05.030 --> 11:06.480
down to your hands.

11:07.320 --> 11:08.150
So?

11:11.910 --> 11:13.270
You don't have long left.

11:13.270 --> 11:14.270
In that case,

11:14.640 --> 11:16.160
I won't trouble you.

11:16.350 --> 11:17.950
Release my pressure points.

11:20.600 --> 11:21.550
Release it.

11:33.730 --> 11:36.060
I‘m going back
to Tianlang Pass tomorrow.

11:36.390 --> 11:38.630
So, I'll give you a big gift today.

11:39.050 --> 11:40.050
Is this a gift,

11:41.120 --> 11:42.000
or revenge?

11:52.910 --> 11:54.910
Who exactly is being interrogated?

11:55.240 --> 11:56.970
Should I go over and take a look?

12:00.270 --> 12:01.030
Forget it.

12:01.360 --> 12:03.000
I'd better not disturb him.

12:05.030 --> 12:05.670
Go back!

12:14.790 --> 12:17.120
General Xiao, you can't even walk now?

12:17.440 --> 12:19.790
You said you would escort me
out of Tianlang Pass tomorrow.

12:19.790 --> 12:20.990
I always keep my word.

12:21.910 --> 12:24.320
Alright, then go out by yourself.

12:44.320 --> 12:45.150
Huang Jian.

12:46.510 --> 12:47.360
Huang Jian!

12:51.500 --> 12:52.870
Drink.

12:54.720 --> 12:55.480
Come on.

13:00.310 --> 13:01.470
It's getting late.

13:02.030 --> 13:03.890
I need to enter the pass tomorrow.

13:04.050 --> 13:05.960
Miss, rest early.

13:09.130 --> 13:09.760
By the way.

13:15.060 --> 13:16.720
Here is the money for the wine.

13:28.030 --> 13:29.360
You're

13:29.550 --> 13:31.320
very generous.

13:31.670 --> 13:33.080
This gold

13:33.440 --> 13:35.640
is enough to buy all the wine I have here.

13:35.730 --> 13:37.010
Then consider it

13:37.190 --> 13:38.590
that I've bought

13:38.620 --> 13:39.700
out all your wine.

13:40.360 --> 13:41.410
When the day comes,

13:41.410 --> 13:43.140
I'll have a good drink with you.

13:56.000 --> 13:56.600
General,

13:56.620 --> 13:57.860
are you feeling better?

13:57.860 --> 13:58.770
Much better.

13:59.270 --> 14:02.000
You look much better than before.

14:02.240 --> 14:04.850
It seems Dr. Ling is quite capable.

14:05.270 --> 14:06.240
Why do you still want to send

14:06.240 --> 14:08.220
her back to Changmo tomorrow?

14:09.340 --> 14:10.470
I've made up my mind.

14:11.360 --> 14:13.730
Send her back to Changmo tomorrow morning.

14:13.730 --> 14:14.850
Report, General!

14:15.200 --> 14:17.930
The patrol squad is fighting
with Changmo's men.

14:19.600 --> 14:20.400
General Xiao.

14:21.090 --> 14:21.640
I'm fine.

14:22.750 --> 14:24.810
Let's go to the city gate tower first.

14:25.460 --> 14:28.190
General Xiao, I brought
the medicinal wine here.

14:30.410 --> 14:31.290
Physician Han.

14:31.710 --> 14:33.170
Just leave it here for now.

14:36.440 --> 14:38.600
Something happened at the city gate tower.

14:38.600 --> 14:39.930
I need to go check it out.

14:40.060 --> 14:41.670
Given your current condition,

14:41.670 --> 14:43.670
you shouldn't move around too much.

14:44.440 --> 14:45.750
If you insist on going,

14:45.770 --> 14:47.170
let me come with you

14:47.210 --> 14:48.690
in case of any emergency.

14:49.450 --> 14:51.110
How could that possibly work?

14:53.840 --> 14:54.970
With your identity,

14:56.440 --> 14:57.890
it's not appropriate
for you to enter the camp.

14:57.890 --> 14:58.600
I...

14:59.370 --> 15:01.980
What danger could a woman like me
possibly pose?

15:01.980 --> 15:03.980
Besides, your health is important.

15:04.580 --> 15:06.710
I don't want to see the treatment fail.

15:07.910 --> 15:09.000
Report!

15:09.720 --> 15:11.740
General, the Changmo army
used custom-made caltrops.

15:11.740 --> 15:12.680
The wounded are in unbearable pain.

15:12.680 --> 15:13.910
The medical camp sent me
to ask for your permission

15:13.910 --> 15:15.060
to use opium for pain relief.

15:15.060 --> 15:16.680
Go ahead. Why even ask about
such a small matter?

15:16.680 --> 15:17.350
No.

15:18.090 --> 15:19.870
Opium is highly addictive if overused.

15:19.870 --> 15:20.630
I have a way.

15:20.870 --> 15:22.750
Right, Dr. Ling is from Changmo.

15:22.770 --> 15:24.170
She must have a solution.

15:24.360 --> 15:26.510
General, I know about these caltrops.

15:26.850 --> 15:28.050
Besides, as a doctor,

15:28.080 --> 15:29.590
I wouldn't refuse to save the wounded

15:29.590 --> 15:31.590
just because they are from Jinglan.

15:43.760 --> 15:45.030
So many people are injured.

15:45.030 --> 15:46.160
Apply the medicine!

15:47.970 --> 15:48.570
Let me see.

15:48.830 --> 15:50.010
The Changmo people are treacherous.

15:50.010 --> 15:51.210
They injured our brothers.

15:51.210 --> 15:52.240
General, she...

15:52.440 --> 15:53.940
Saving people is the priority now.

15:53.940 --> 15:56.000
I would never gamble with your lives.

16:03.920 --> 16:04.710
Bear with it.

16:12.750 --> 16:13.390
Hold on.

16:15.120 --> 16:15.950
Hold on.

16:16.220 --> 16:16.950
Bear with it.

16:18.070 --> 16:18.950
Bear with it.

16:28.320 --> 16:29.240
Hold on.

16:35.330 --> 16:36.090
That's it.

16:36.980 --> 16:38.440
Thank you, Physician Han.

16:39.740 --> 16:40.750
-Next one.
-Okay.

16:41.020 --> 16:41.610
This way.

16:51.870 --> 16:52.730
Physician Han.

16:55.030 --> 16:56.440
Thanks for your help this time.

16:56.440 --> 16:57.440
It was no trouble.

16:59.790 --> 17:01.190
You helped out this time.

17:01.840 --> 17:02.670
Could it be...

17:04.750 --> 17:07.280
A healer doesn't ask
about one's background.

17:07.400 --> 17:08.720
I just want to do my best

17:09.280 --> 17:10.410
to help more people.

17:11.270 --> 17:12.700
But they are Jinglan people.

17:12.700 --> 17:14.359
What if they're Jinglan people?

17:14.359 --> 17:15.910
And what if they're Changmo people?

17:15.910 --> 17:17.069
In my eyes,

17:17.270 --> 17:20.109
there is only health and sickness.

17:21.470 --> 17:22.800
If everyone in the world

17:22.910 --> 17:24.220
were like you,

17:24.720 --> 17:25.849
that would be great.

17:28.450 --> 17:30.180
If only the world were at peace,

17:30.300 --> 17:32.900
and everyone could live unharmed.

17:42.580 --> 17:43.540
Will there ever be a day

17:43.540 --> 17:44.940
when the world is at peace

17:45.630 --> 17:47.590
and free from illness and disaster?

17:47.590 --> 17:48.590
Of course it will.

17:57.130 --> 17:57.960
What's wrong?

17:58.060 --> 17:59.390
Are you feeling unwell?

18:00.680 --> 18:01.440
No.

18:04.610 --> 18:07.070
I just remembered some things
from the past.

18:08.780 --> 18:09.640
If you're fine,

18:09.650 --> 18:10.520
I'll be going.

18:11.260 --> 18:11.980
Miss Han.

18:13.760 --> 18:14.470
Thank you

18:16.190 --> 18:16.910
this time.

18:55.750 --> 18:56.310
Go.

19:01.110 --> 19:02.480
Good.

19:03.030 --> 19:04.440
Good, good.

19:07.240 --> 19:09.070
Everyone, count down from 3 with me.

19:09.070 --> 19:09.960
3,

19:10.110 --> 19:11.110
2,

19:11.310 --> 19:12.720
1!

19:17.070 --> 19:19.670
Any other folks want to give it a try?

19:19.690 --> 19:20.620
This young lady.

19:21.000 --> 19:21.680
Come, miss.

19:21.680 --> 19:22.610
That young lady.

19:22.680 --> 19:23.440
Don't leave.

19:24.160 --> 19:25.850
Yes, you. Come on.

19:27.840 --> 19:29.070
-Miss, don't worry.
-What are you doing?

19:29.070 --> 19:29.890
It's absolutely safe.

19:29.890 --> 19:30.920
-It's a family secret trick.
-Stop pulling me.

19:30.920 --> 19:32.240
It's completely safe.

19:32.350 --> 19:33.390
It's completely safe.

19:33.390 --> 19:33.710
I...

19:33.730 --> 19:34.650
It's completely safe.

19:34.650 --> 19:35.410
Don't worry.

19:36.880 --> 19:38.050
Open the door.

19:38.920 --> 19:40.030
Open the door!

19:40.810 --> 19:42.400
Folks,

19:42.430 --> 19:43.780
keep your eyes wide open,

19:43.780 --> 19:45.300
hold your breath,

19:45.420 --> 19:47.020
and count down from 3 with me.

19:47.260 --> 19:48.020
3.

19:48.550 --> 19:49.830
2.

19:50.020 --> 19:51.410
1!

19:55.290 --> 19:58.090
Good!

19:58.450 --> 19:59.450
That's amazing.

20:06.250 --> 20:08.010
Folks.

20:08.040 --> 20:10.440
Anyone else want
to come up and give it a try?

20:10.790 --> 20:12.110
If not,

20:12.130 --> 20:13.780
we'll wrap it up here.

20:15.240 --> 20:16.440
What's going on?

20:16.470 --> 20:17.800
Is she coming out or not?

20:18.750 --> 20:20.290
Where is the girl from just now?

20:20.290 --> 20:21.600
Which girl?

20:22.130 --> 20:23.750
The girl who just went in.

20:24.510 --> 20:25.550
I didn't see her.

20:25.860 --> 20:26.540
Open it.

20:27.380 --> 20:27.990
This...

20:35.920 --> 20:36.920
Let's go.

20:36.950 --> 20:38.540
They are running away.

20:40.020 --> 20:41.020
Let me out!

20:41.310 --> 20:42.350
Let me out!

20:42.900 --> 20:44.450
Let me out now!

20:45.060 --> 20:46.610
Let me out!

21:06.370 --> 21:07.130
Stop!

21:16.630 --> 21:17.160
Yunling.

21:17.400 --> 21:17.930
Yunling.

21:19.940 --> 21:20.470
Yunling!

21:21.890 --> 21:22.400
Don't.

21:22.520 --> 21:23.070
Don't.

21:23.210 --> 21:23.790
Don't.

21:25.000 --> 21:25.640
It's me.

21:25.870 --> 21:26.720
I'm Xiao Chi.

21:39.810 --> 21:40.830
I-It's alright now.

21:40.830 --> 21:41.830
It's alright now.

21:46.500 --> 21:47.360
Physician Han.

21:47.810 --> 21:50.540
General asked me
to bring you this farewell wine.

21:50.740 --> 21:51.300
He said

21:51.500 --> 21:52.930
you were frightened today.

21:52.930 --> 21:54.050
This is to help you settle your nerves

21:54.050 --> 21:55.050
and help you rest.

21:55.680 --> 21:56.280
By the way,

21:56.680 --> 21:58.510
General Xiao has military affairs
to handle,

21:58.510 --> 22:00.170
so he won't come to bother you.

22:03.550 --> 22:04.350
General Xiao.

22:04.450 --> 22:06.580
Are you really sending Miss Ling back?

22:06.670 --> 22:09.000
Haven't you always suspected she's a spy?

22:09.180 --> 22:09.710
General.

22:09.760 --> 22:11.060
Actually, I think she...

22:11.060 --> 22:11.920
That's enough.

22:13.440 --> 22:14.570
Let's do it this way.

22:18.880 --> 22:19.850
Miss Ling.

22:20.520 --> 22:21.580
General Xiao said,

22:21.750 --> 22:22.750
tomorrow...

22:23.030 --> 22:26.160
tomorrow, he will personally
escort you out of the city.

22:42.270 --> 22:43.030
Good!

22:43.610 --> 22:45.780
It seems you're recovering well.

22:46.480 --> 22:49.340
Isn't it because
of your treatment, Physician Han?

22:50.420 --> 22:51.720
Just call me Han Yunling.

22:51.720 --> 22:53.480
Then how should I thank you, Miss Han?

22:53.480 --> 22:54.440
Getting better soon

22:54.440 --> 22:56.960
would be the greatest thanks
you could give me.

22:56.960 --> 22:58.550
I won't just recover quickly.

22:58.550 --> 23:00.270
I will also go to battle,

23:00.270 --> 23:01.480
protect the people of Jinglan,

23:01.480 --> 23:02.750
and protect you.

23:05.720 --> 23:07.780
I don't know if you still remember me.

23:08.660 --> 23:10.790
But since I promised to protect you,

23:12.410 --> 23:13.060
then...

23:13.480 --> 23:15.880
sending you away
from this place of trouble

23:17.030 --> 23:18.960
is perhaps a kind of protection.

23:25.810 --> 23:26.870
Fine, I'll go back.

23:27.820 --> 23:29.950
I will definitely think of another way

23:29.980 --> 23:31.040
to save my brother.

23:39.000 --> 23:39.800
General Xiao.

23:40.680 --> 23:41.480
General Xiao.

23:42.680 --> 23:43.280
General Xiao.

23:43.280 --> 23:44.080
General Xiao.

23:44.250 --> 23:46.980
Are you really sending
Miss Ling back to Changmo?

23:47.400 --> 23:48.240
Yes.

23:48.260 --> 23:49.710
Maybe you should reconsider.

23:49.710 --> 23:50.230
Lu Li.

23:50.800 --> 23:52.330
In the past, no matter
what decision I made,

23:52.330 --> 23:54.190
you would obey unconditionally.

23:54.210 --> 23:55.210
What's wrong with you today?

23:55.210 --> 23:56.270
Well, it's just...

23:56.550 --> 23:57.680
Enough. Say no more.

23:57.710 --> 23:58.710
My mind is made up.

24:00.490 --> 24:01.690
Where is Han Yunling?

24:01.950 --> 24:02.590
I'll go look for her.

24:02.590 --> 24:03.790
No need to look for me.

24:09.480 --> 24:11.310
Don't you want to send me back?

24:11.880 --> 24:12.680
Let's go.

24:12.720 --> 24:14.580
Send me back to Changmo right now.

24:15.370 --> 24:16.500
What's wrong with you?

24:16.500 --> 24:17.340
General Xiao,

24:17.380 --> 24:18.170
I suspect

24:18.200 --> 24:20.980
it's because of the wine
you had me send her last night.

24:20.980 --> 24:22.700
That wasn't strong wine.

24:22.980 --> 24:23.700
It can't be.

24:24.440 --> 24:26.230
Are we going or not?

24:27.330 --> 24:29.360
I'll grant your wish right now.

24:29.440 --> 24:31.300
I can't stay here another second.

24:31.960 --> 24:32.570
Fine.

24:33.340 --> 24:34.860
We'll settle this when I'm back.

24:34.860 --> 24:35.590
Keep an eye on her.

24:35.590 --> 24:36.240
Let's go.

24:36.390 --> 24:37.820
In broad daylight,

24:37.840 --> 24:39.230
General Xiao,
you have such refined tastes.

24:39.230 --> 24:39.780
Don't stop me!

24:39.780 --> 24:40.300
Zheng?

24:40.320 --> 24:41.350
Physician Han, don't go over there.

24:41.350 --> 24:43.090
-What brings you here?
-I want to go out!

24:43.090 --> 24:44.610
His Majesty sent me to see

24:45.070 --> 24:46.630
-what exactly you've been up to
-Don't touch me.

24:46.630 --> 24:47.700
all these years at Tianlang Pass.

24:47.700 --> 24:48.600
You can't go there, Physician Han.

24:48.600 --> 24:49.460
Physician Han.

24:49.790 --> 24:50.270
Physician Han.

24:50.270 --> 24:51.480
You've even learned
to force innocent women now?

24:51.480 --> 24:52.280
Don't stop me.

24:52.290 --> 24:53.040
Let me take you back to your room.

24:53.040 --> 24:54.610
Zheng, listen to me.

24:56.100 --> 24:57.170
No need to explain.

24:57.200 --> 24:58.830
No, it's really nothing.

24:59.330 --> 24:59.830
Physician Han.

24:59.830 --> 25:00.650
Keep a close eye on her.

25:00.650 --> 25:01.490
Report!

25:03.550 --> 25:04.350
General Xiao,

25:04.390 --> 25:06.290
a Changmo general is challenging us
outside the pass.

25:06.290 --> 25:07.920
Seems I arrived just in time.

25:08.250 --> 25:09.240
There's a good show to watch.

25:09.240 --> 25:10.300
Zheng, then please

25:10.530 --> 25:11.610
cheer for me.

25:11.860 --> 25:12.450
Alright.

25:15.440 --> 25:16.440
Keep an eye on her.

25:16.510 --> 25:17.310
Wait for my return.

25:17.310 --> 25:18.270
Yes.

25:20.010 --> 25:21.960
[Shengde Gate]

25:23.570 --> 25:26.290
The marriage alliance is a major event.

25:26.640 --> 25:28.960
We mustn't decide this in haste.

25:28.990 --> 25:31.030
Precisely because it's a major event,

25:31.030 --> 25:33.750
Your Majesty should make a decision soon.

25:33.830 --> 25:37.350
I already sent Fei Zheng to Tianlang Pass

25:37.490 --> 25:40.300
to see what Changmo's intentions are.

25:40.330 --> 25:41.240
Your Majesty.

25:41.600 --> 25:43.120
In my opinion,

25:43.140 --> 25:46.180
Changmo just wants
to make peace with Jinglan.

25:46.550 --> 25:48.850
They wouldn't dare
have any other intentions.

25:48.850 --> 25:50.350
Your Majesty worries too much.

25:50.350 --> 25:51.350
Your Majesty.

25:51.410 --> 25:53.000
You are the Emperor.

25:53.020 --> 25:55.090
Your personal affairs
are matters of state.

25:55.090 --> 25:57.090
You must not be careless.

25:57.350 --> 25:58.830
You are still young.

25:59.390 --> 26:00.670
The three of us

26:00.950 --> 26:04.910
are the core ministers entrusted
to you by the late Emperor.

26:05.360 --> 26:08.880
You must trust his judgment.

26:08.930 --> 26:10.260
Yes, Your Majesty.

26:13.600 --> 26:16.050
The Eldest Princess has arrived.

26:26.110 --> 26:29.240
Greetings, Eldest Princess.

26:42.440 --> 26:44.570
I heard today's court discussion

26:44.680 --> 26:47.510
is about the marriage alliance
between Jinglan and Changmo.

26:47.510 --> 26:49.870
So I specially came to listen.

26:51.790 --> 26:55.910
The marriage alliance document
from Changmo has been here for days.

26:56.000 --> 26:59.960
We just hope His Majesty
makes a decision soon.

26:59.960 --> 27:02.440
The marriage alliance
between Jinglan and Changmo

27:02.440 --> 27:05.400
concerns the peace of both nations
and the lives of the people.

27:05.400 --> 27:07.160
This cannot be taken lightly.

27:07.160 --> 27:09.210
Even if my father were alive,

27:09.230 --> 27:11.510
he would consider it carefully.

27:11.640 --> 27:13.400
His Majesty is not yet married.

27:13.420 --> 27:15.570
We does not have an empress yet.

27:15.600 --> 27:18.310
If he takes a Princess of Changmo
into the palace first,

27:18.310 --> 27:21.030
and she gives birth to a child,

27:21.030 --> 27:23.220
the royal bloodline may be compromised.

27:23.220 --> 27:25.670
Do you all agree?

27:25.720 --> 27:28.850
We believe every word Your Highness
said is reasonable.

27:28.870 --> 27:29.980
Of course.

27:30.010 --> 27:33.010
The Emperor's marriage is a major event.

27:33.030 --> 27:34.690
As for when the marriage will take place,

27:34.690 --> 27:36.610
we still have to listen to His Majesty.

27:36.610 --> 27:38.260
Once His Majesty decides,

27:38.370 --> 27:40.060
I will spare no expense.

27:40.080 --> 27:43.720
When the time comes, I will open
the treasury and allocate ample funds

27:43.720 --> 27:45.680
to handle this matter properly.

27:46.290 --> 27:47.770
What

27:47.920 --> 27:49.920
do the three of you think?

27:53.240 --> 27:55.920
We will follow
the Eldest Princess's orders.

28:03.600 --> 28:05.070
What does it say?

28:13.430 --> 28:15.760
If the princess sent for the alliance
is not well protected,

28:15.760 --> 28:17.290
Jinglan will be destroyed?

28:19.750 --> 28:20.810
His Majesty sent me

28:20.810 --> 28:22.330
for the marriage alliance

28:22.710 --> 28:24.990
to uncover Changmo's true intentions.

28:25.790 --> 28:27.480
This way, we can be prepared.

28:27.830 --> 28:29.000
Rest assured, Zheng.

28:29.000 --> 28:31.260
I will definitely defend Tianlang Pass.

28:32.790 --> 28:34.120
With General Xiao here,

28:34.270 --> 28:35.590
how can I not be at ease?

28:44.640 --> 28:46.240
Take me out of the pass!

28:46.970 --> 28:48.230
How much did she drink?

28:48.350 --> 28:49.360
It's already this late,

28:49.360 --> 28:50.840
and she's still not sober.

28:51.400 --> 28:53.020
Take me out of the pass!

28:57.450 --> 28:58.650
May I ask,

28:59.110 --> 29:01.310
who exactly is this girl?

29:02.710 --> 29:04.310
My name is Han Yunling.

29:05.030 --> 29:07.070
I am a physician from Changmo.

29:07.390 --> 29:08.950
I saved his life.

29:09.550 --> 29:11.150
But he won't listen to me

29:11.170 --> 29:12.900
and even wants to drive me away.

29:15.870 --> 29:17.800
I won't leave. I won't leave.

29:17.820 --> 29:19.450
I will definitely cure you.

29:19.480 --> 29:21.280
You also said
you would escort me to the capital.

29:21.280 --> 29:22.590
You promised me.

29:28.720 --> 29:29.270
I...

29:30.030 --> 29:30.590
This...

29:33.330 --> 29:34.580
Judging by your complexion,

29:34.580 --> 29:36.340
you look much better

29:36.570 --> 29:37.700
than when we parted.

29:38.570 --> 29:40.810
It seems she has some skills.

29:41.890 --> 29:44.120
What a pity that the imperial physician
His Majesty sent with me

29:44.120 --> 29:45.970
won't be needed.

29:48.200 --> 29:49.290
She is skilled.

29:54.240 --> 29:54.880
But she

29:56.130 --> 29:57.160
is from Changmo.

29:57.720 --> 29:59.380
So what if she is from Changmo?

29:59.830 --> 30:01.360
Our countries
have been at war for years,

30:01.360 --> 30:02.030
and I

30:02.340 --> 30:03.540
guard Tianlang Pass.

30:03.960 --> 30:05.270
So that's

30:05.550 --> 30:07.480
why you're sending her away today?

30:10.750 --> 30:12.010
You're afraid she'll poison you

30:12.010 --> 30:12.930
and harm you?

30:13.500 --> 30:14.300
She won't.

30:14.760 --> 30:16.290
Then what are you afraid of?

30:17.720 --> 30:19.450
Not everyone in Changmo is bad.

30:19.640 --> 30:21.900
Since she can cure your chronic illness,

30:22.000 --> 30:23.200
why not keep her here?

30:26.070 --> 30:27.550
Looking at it this way,

30:27.880 --> 30:29.400
you two are quite a match.

30:30.440 --> 30:31.030
Zheng,

30:31.830 --> 30:33.030
what are you talking about?

30:33.030 --> 30:35.110
I'm saying exactly what I mean.

30:35.300 --> 30:36.360
It's settled then.

30:36.490 --> 30:37.770
Keep her here

30:37.800 --> 30:39.260
to continue treating you.

30:39.680 --> 30:40.770
It won't be considered colluding
with the enemy.

30:40.770 --> 30:41.770
You have my word.

30:42.350 --> 30:43.240
How could that possibly work?

30:43.240 --> 30:44.350
Why not?

30:44.510 --> 30:45.110
Tomorrow,

30:45.560 --> 30:48.170
I'll have the imperial physician,
who hasn't left the palace in a long time,

30:48.170 --> 30:49.650
watch her treat you.

30:49.820 --> 30:51.620
Let him learn something from it.

30:53.070 --> 30:53.880
Zheng.

30:54.040 --> 30:54.580
I...

30:57.200 --> 30:58.960
I haven't seen Chu in a long time.

30:58.960 --> 31:00.680
I wonder how he's doing.

31:01.640 --> 31:02.640
His Majesty.

31:04.190 --> 31:04.880
He...

31:05.480 --> 31:06.530
is doing well.
